                  <msItem>
                     <p> BLOUNTESHAL. <persName>
                           <forename>Roger</forename> de <surname>Billingford</surname>
                        </persName> grants 
                  to the <orgName key="org_106005">church of St. Mary and St. Nicholas of Tipetre</orgName>, for the souls of himself, his 
                  ancestors and successors, the homage and whole of the service which 
                  <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename>, <surname type="patronymic">son of Goding</surname>
                        </persName>, was
                  accustomed to pay to the said Roger for three acres of land in <placeName key="place_106049">Blunteshale</placeName> which
                  he held of him. (<origDate when="1220" precision="low">c. 1220</origDate>.) 
